      <hr />
      <div class="formatname">MARC 21 Bibliographic - full</div>
      <div class="datename">October 2010</div>
      <hr />
      <h4>Indicators and Subfield Codes</h4>
      <div class="wildcard">
         <div>
            <p>Has no indicators or subfield codes; the data elements are positionally defined.</p>
         </div>
      </div>
